      <title>瑞士同意与欧盟达成协议，重建 2021 年破裂后的关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/switzerland-agrees-eu-deal-rebuilding-ties-after-2021-breakdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过漫长而紧张的谈判，瑞士与欧盟在年底前达成协议，确保瑞士能够进入欧盟单一市场，该协议也非官方敲定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/switzerland-agrees-eu-deal-rebuilding-ties-after-2021-breakdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 13:14:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
